#Linux Academy

1. Install Jenkins
2. Configure Firewall
	add port 8080/tcp


3. Set up Proxy server
		Install nginx server
		config {
			location /{
							Add Jenkins location
			}
		}
4. restart service systmctl start nginx service

5. hit url from browser

6. unlock Jenkins : input adminstrator Password

7. Create user adminstrator

 8. $ getent passwd jenkins //command  to  see the Jenkins   passwd
 
 9. $sudo passwd Jenkins //command to change password
 
 10. $visudo  // add jenkins access
 
 11. ssh-copy-id jenkins@serverIP
 
 
